org.gvsig.chart

Interface GroupedCharts

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Cloneable, Observable, Persistent
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    OverlayChart

    public interface GroupedCharts
extends Observable, Persistent, Cloneable
    This interfaces defines an specific characteristics to a ChartService to be used as a container of other ChartServices. It let us to overlay them in a unique chart sharing axis, legends, etc.
    See Also:
    ChartService
